          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-journal-text me-2"></i>Simple Ledger</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Add transactions fast. Clear running balance. CSV in/out when you need it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow me-2"></i>At-a-glance</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Recent activity and totals without clicking through 10 pages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-2"></i>Private by default</h5>
